How about more flaming of the Wrath spells?<br>
22pp?<br>
<br>
Does Verant think hitting for 2000 is unbalancing?<br>
What it means is Verant thinks we are fine and any more power is unbalancing.<br>
DD is too powerful in and of itself.<br>
We cannot be allowed to contribute at least equally.<br>
